Fàbregas starred in his own one-time only television programme, called ''"The Cesc Fàbregas Show: Nike Live"'', that aired on 19 May 2008. The programme was sponsored by [[Nike, Inc.|Nike]] and was shown on [[Sky Sports]]. The show featured Fàbregas in several sketches with Arsenal teammates like [[Philippe Senderos]] and [[Nicklas Bendtner]], as well as coach [[Arsène Wenger]], Fàbregas's parents and ''[[Little Britain]]'' star [[Matt Lucas]].<ref>[http://inside.nike.com/blogs/nikefootball-en_SG/tags/nikelive?view=all NIKELIVE], NikeLiveFabregas.com, accessed 19 April 2008.</ref>

